del-item-with-attachment.xpi
Deletes Zotero items along with their associated attachments (including linked files), preventing orphaned files in the library.
删除 Zotero 条目时同步删除关联附件（含链接文件），避免文献库中出现孤立文件。


zotero-pdf-rename.xpi
Renames PDF attachments using custom rules based on bibliographic information (e.g., Author_Year_Title), standardizing file naming conventions.
根据文献元数据（如作者_年份_标题）按自定义规则重命名 PDF 附件，规范文件命名。


zotero-attanger.xpi
An advanced attachment manager supporting automatic renaming, moving, and syncing of PDF files, replacing ZotFile for Zotero 7+.
高级附件管理器，支持 PDF 文件自动重命名、移动和同步，替代 ZotFile 适配 Zotero 7 及以上版本。

sci-pdf.xpi
Integrates Sci-Hub resolvers to automatically download full-text PDFs for literature items missing attachments.
集成 Sci-Hub 解析器，自动为缺失附件的文献条目下载全文 PDF。
